545
00:41:51.966 --> 00:41:54.766
<i># I cannot see the reason</i>

546
00:41:54.846 --> 00:41:58.366
<i># But maybe knowing "I don't know"</i>

547
00:41:58.446 --> 00:42:01.966
<i># Is part of getting through</i>

548
00:42:03.166 --> 00:42:06.366
<i># I try to do what's best</i>

549
00:42:06.446 --> 00:42:09.646
<i># And faith has made it easy</i>

550
00:42:09.726 --> 00:42:13.886
<i># To see the best thing I can do</i>

551
00:42:13.966 --> 00:42:16.846
<i># Is put my trust in you</i>

552
00:42:16.926 --> 00:42:20.926
<i># For you know</i>

553
00:42:21.006 --> 00:42:24.486
<i># Better than I</i>

554
