<i># The seasons fly</i>

652
00:51:30.006 --> 00:51:34.086
<i># A man stands where a boy once stood</i>

653
00:51:35.686 --> 00:51:37.886
<i># His path unfolds</i>

654
00:51:37.966 --> 00:51:41.606
<i># And unafraid he walks in service</i>

